thereby giving 3m the right, but not the obligation, to maintain a presence in
a leased facility. 3ms primary capital lease, which became effective in april2003,
involves a building in the united kingdom (with a lease term of 22 years).
during the second quarter of 2003, 3m recorded a capital lease asset and
obligation of approximately 33.5 million united kingdom pounds (approximately
$67 million at december31, 2007 exchange rates). minimum lease payments
