corporate investment gains and losses, certain derivative gains and losses,
insurance-related gains and losses, certain litigation expenses, corporate
restructuring program charges and other miscellaneous items. because this
category includes a variety of miscellaneous items, it is subject to
fluctuation on a quarterly and annual basis.
